the cookbook app

Create a cookbook recipe app
1 page for all the ingridients with a checker mark
1 page for instructions
    hability to see one instruction at a time or all together
Possibility to add new recipes
Possibility to export the ingridients to a to-do list or email or text message
Possibility to import and export recipes to a data-base
Possibility to send the recipe to a friend by email, text message, others and internal app
Possibility to see images